She&rsquo;s also still close with the members of I.O.I. &ldquo;At MAMA (Mnet Asian Music Awards) this year, I was reminded of when I.O.I first performed together. The members and I talked about it, too.&rdquo;<br />
<br />
Chungha revealed that the I.O.I members were the first to hear her upcoming song. &ldquo;Doyeon and Yoojung said they wanted to listen again and cheered me on, asking me to make my comeback soon. When my teaser photo came out, Yeonjung made it her profile picture. I was so thankful.&rdquo;

【新聞】190102 請夏 &ldquo;全昭彌 正在準備solo出道...和I.O.I成員每天都有聯繫&rdquo;<br />
請夏說&ldquo;Somi過得很好 她​​是快樂病毒也是維他som&rdquo; &ldquo;好奇她過得怎樣 然後給我展示了她做的曲 感覺和音樂合為一體了&rdquo;<br />
而且&ldquo;Somi既作曲又作詞很有才華在大眾面前還沒出道可能沒能展示自己真的是個很有才的孩子&rdquo; &ldquo;Somi是我以後也很想試著作曲的情況(如果以solo出道)會做的很棒的我也很期待&rdquo;
